data.description: Welcome to your beachside oasis! This delightful bungalow, boasting 2 master bedrooms and 2 baths, offers the perfect coastal retreat just two blocks away from the renowned World's Most Famous Beach.Located in the heart of Daytona Beach, this home is surrounded by attractions. Enjoy leisurely strolls to The Ocean Walk Shoppes, where shopping, restaurants, and a movie theater await. Daytona Lagoon is just a stone's throw away, offering endless fun, and the iconic bandshell is within easy reach. Inside, the kitchen is a culinary delight with its granite countertops and a convenient gas stove.The outdoor shed houses the washer and dryer, providing ample storage for all your beach toys and essentials. Relax and unwind on your screened-in porch,featuring newly installed windows,creating a cozy all-season space. The yard is fenced in. Don't miss your chance to own this charming beachside gem - schedule a viewing today and experience the coastal lifestyle at its best! Square footage from tax rolls. All information is intended to be accurate but can't be guaranteed.
